(283, 1, '2018-04-08 20:18:21', '2018-04-08 20:18:21', '<div class="summarycontent 2coltitlecontent">\r\n<h3>Room Details</h3>\r\nOccupying a generous 32 to 41sqm (344 to 441sq-ft), the Superior Rooms at our hotel in Manila offer the perfect fusion of comfort and convenience. Enjoy views of Manila Bay, the city skyline or the tranquil outdoor <a href="https://www.panpacific.com/en/hotels-resorts/philippines/manila/stay/facilities/swimming-pool.html" target="_blank">Swimming Pool</a>, or simply relax with the modern multimedia system and interactive flat-screen television. Guests who need to stay connected can make the most of the complimentary Internet access and executive work desk, while guests who need to unwind will enjoy the spacious ensuite bathroom, complete with an indulgent rain shower and premium amenities.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="2coltitlecontent inroomamenities">\r\n<h3>In-room Amenities</h3>\r\n<div class="row">\r\n<div class="l-half-col">\r\n<div><b>For Your Comfort</b></div>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>A choice of king-sized or twin beds</li>\r\n 	<li>Pillow menu</li>\r\n 	<li>Executive writing table and stationery set</li>\r\n 	<li>Ensuite bathroom with separate rain shower stall and bathtub</li>\r\n 	<li>Bathrobe, slippers and hairdryer</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<div><b>For Your Convenience</b></div>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Wired and wireless high-speed Internet access</li>\r\n 	<li>Spare electrical outlet and power adapter</li>\r\n 	<li>IDD telephone and voice mail</li>\r\n 	<li>Complimentary local phone calls</li>\r\n 	<li>Secure key-card access</li>\r\n 	<li>Personal digital safe</li>\r\n 	<li>Iron and ironing board</li>\r\n 	<li>24-hour in-room dining</li>\r\n 	<li>Butler and daily turn-down service</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="l-half-col">\r\n<div><b>For Your Indulgence</b></div>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>32” LCD interactive television with local and cable channels</li>\r\n 	<li>DVD player</li>\r\n 	<li>Fully-stocked minibar</li>\r\n 	<li>Coffee and tea making facilities</li>\r\n 	<li>Complimentary bottled water</li>\r\n 	<li>Daily newspaper</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<iframe style="border: 0;" src="https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d13690.657663510854!2d-0.12675282307727212!3d5.813354182600511!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0xfdf798769820e8f%3A0x2c5f5fde00a3434d!2sOyibi!5e1!3m2!1sen!2sgh!4v1523067210316" width="1100" height="450" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen="allowfullscreen"></iframe>', 'Nsemka Room', 'Experience understated elegance in a Superior Room at our Manila hotel, complete with the choice of a king-sized bed or twin beds, a spacious ensuite bathroom and complimentary Internet access.', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '90-autosave-v1', '', '', '2018-04-08 20:18:21', '2018-04-08 20:18:21', '', 90, 'http://localhost/ieahouse/index.php/2018/04/08/90-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
