(337, 1, '2018-04-19 05:21:29', '2018-04-19 05:21:29', '<div class="2coltitlecontent inroomamenities">\n<div class="row">\n<div class="l-half-col">\n<ul>\n 	<li>\n<div class="summarycontent 2coltitlecontent">\n<h3>Room Details</h3>\nExperience personalised service and hospitality when you book a stay in a Odadie Room in our IEA Guesthouse. Offering added space and comfort, these thoughtfully-appointed rooms provide guests with views of Manila Bay and the city, as well as round-the-clock butler service and complimentary Internet access. Find rest and relaxation on the comfortable king-sized bed, or make the most of the multimedia hub, complete with an interactive television and a DVD player. When you are ready to explore, the comprehensive offering of <a href="https://www.panpacific.com/en/hotels-resorts/philippines/manila/stay/facilities.html" target="_blank">Facilities &amp; Services</a> at our hotel in Manila awaits, including a well-equipped <a href="https://www.panpacific.com/en/hotels-resorts/philippines/manila/stay/facilities/vip-gym.html" target="_blank">Fitness Centre</a>, a modern <a href="https://www.panpacific.com/en/hotels-resorts/philippines/manila/stay/facilities/business-centre.html" target="_blank">Business Centre</a> and a refreshing outdoor <a href="https://www.panpacific.com/en/hotels-resorts/philippines/manila/stay/facilities/swimming-pool.html" target="_blank">Swimming Pool</a>.\n\n</div>\n<div class="2coltitlecontent inroomamenities">\n<h3>In-Room Amenities</h3>\n<div class="row">\n<div class="l-half-col">\n<div><b>For Your Comfort</b></div>\n<ul>\n 	<li>King-sized bed</li>\n 	<li>Pillow menu</li>\n 	<li>Executive writing table and stationery set</li>\n 	<li>Ensuite bathroom with separate rain shower stall and bathtub</li>\n 	<li>Bathrobe, slippers and hairdryer</li>\n</ul>\n<div><b>For Your Convenience</b></div>\n<ul>\n 	<li>Wired and wireless high-speed Internet access</li>\n 	<li>Spare electrical outlet and power adapter</li>\n 	<li>IDD telephone and voice mail</li>\n 	<li>Complimentary local phone calls</li>\n 	<li>Secure key-card access</li>\n 	<li>Personal digital safe</li>\n 	<li>Iron and ironing board</li>\n 	<li>24-hour in-room dining</li>\n 	<li>Butler and daily turn-down service</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<div class="l-half-col">\n<div><b>For Your Indulgence</b></div>\n<ul>\n 	<li>32” LCD interactive television with local and\ncable channels</li>\n 	<li>Multimedia hub with DVD player</li>\n 	<li>Fully-stocked minibar</li>\n 	<li>Coffee and tea making facilities</li>\n 	<li>Complimentary bottled water</li>\n 	<li>Daily newspaper</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<iframe style="border: 0;" src="https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d13690.657663510854!2d-0.12675282307727212!3d5.813354182600511!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0xfdf798769820e8f%3A0x2c5f5fde00a3434d!2sOyibi!5e1!3m2!1sen!2sgh!4v1523067210316" width="1100" height="450" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen="allowfullscreen"></iframe>', 'Odadie Room', 'Occupying the enviable corner positions at our hotel in Manila, our 51sqm (549sq-ft) Pacific Rooms feature a modern ensuite bathroom, a convenient executive workspace and complimentary Internet access throughout.', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '93-autosave-v1', '', '', '2018-04-19 05:21:29', '2018-04-19 05:21:29', '', 93, 'http://localhost/ieahouse/93-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(338, 1, '2018-04-19 05:24:35', '2018-04-19 05:24:35', '<div class="summarycontent 2coltitlecontent">\n<h3>Room Details</h3>\nWhether you are visiting Oyibi for business or leisure, the Executive Rooms at our hotel near Kas Valley provide a beautiful setting to relax and rejuvenate. Stay connected with a generously-sized executive work desk and access to our on-site <a href="https://www.panpacific.com/en/hotels-resorts/philippines/manila/stay/facilities/business-centre.html" target="_blank">Business Centre</a>, or simply unwind in the luxurious ensuite, complete with a refreshing rain shower and separate bathtub. In the lounge area, a multimedia hub and interactive television helps keep you entertained, while our fully-equipped <a href="https://www.panpacific.com/en/hotels-resorts/philippines/manila/stay/facilities/vip-gym.html" target="_blank">Fitness Centre</a> has everything you need for an invigorating workout during your stay.\n\n</div>\n<div class="2coltitlecontent inroomamenities">\n<h3>In-room Amenities</h3>\n<div class="row">\n<div class="l-half-col">\n<div><b>For Your Comfort</b></div>\n<ul>\n 	<li>A choice of king-sized or twin beds</li>\n 	<li>Pillow menu</li>\n 	<li>Executive writing table and stationery set</li>\n 	<li>Ensuite bathroom with separate rain shower stall and bathtub</li>\n 	<li>Bathrobe, slippers and hairdryer</li>\n</ul>\n<div><b>For Your Convenience</b></div>\n<ul>\n 	<li>Wired and wireless high-speed Internet access</li>\n 	<li>Spare electrical outlet and power adapter</li>\n 	<li>IDD telephone and voice mail</li>\n 	<li>Complimentary local phone calls</li>\n 	<li>Secure key-card access</li>\n 	<li>Personal digital safe</li>\n 	<li>Iron and ironing board</li>\n 	<li>24-hour in-room dining</li>\n 	<li>Butler and daily turn-down service</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<div class="l-half-col">\n<div><b>For Your Indulgence</b></div>\n<ul>\n 	<li>32” LCD interactive television with local and cable channels</li>\n 	<li>Multimedia hub with DVD player</li>\n 	<li>Fully-stocked minibar</li>\n 	<li>Coffee and tea making facilities</li>\n 	<li>Complimentary bottled water</li>\n 	<li>Daily newspaper</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<iframe style="border: 0;" src="https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d13690.657663510854!2d-0.12675282307727212!3d5.813354182600511!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0xfdf798769820e8f%3A0x2c5f5fde00a3434d!2sOyibi!5e1!3m2!1sen!2sgh!4v1523067210316" width="1100" height="450" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen="allowfullscreen"></iframe>', 'Mpienim Room', 'Designed with the modern professional in mind, the spacious 40 to 48sqm (431 to 517sq-ft) Executive Rooms at our hotel near Star City feature the choice of a king-sized bed or twin beds, a spacious ensuite bathroom and a well-appointed workspace with complimentary Internet access.', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '91-autosave-v1', '', '', '2018-04-19 05:24:35', '2018-04-19 05:24:35', '', 91, 'http://localhost/ieahouse/91-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
